| TC ID  | Scenario                 | Expected Result         |
| ------ | ------------------------ | ----------------------- |
| API001 | Valid Token              | 200 Success             |
| API002 | Invalid Token            | 401 Unauthorized        |
| API003 | Missing Mandatory Field  | 400 Bad Request         |
| API004 | Invalid Request Method   | 405 Method Not Allowed  |
| API005 | Response Time Validation | < 3 Seconds             |
| API006 | Schema Validation        | Response matches schema |
